<p class="govuk-body">
  This cost reduction changes the economics of accessibility. Instead of only converting
  the most critical documents, councils can make <em>everything</em> available in Easy Read --
  housing letters, benefits information, health guidance, and more.
</p>

{# Troubleshooting #}
<details class="govuk-details govuk-!-margin-top-6">
  <summary class="govuk-details__summary">
    <span class="govuk-details__summary-text">
      Troubleshooting: Easy Read job taking a long time
    </span>
  </summary>
  <div class="govuk-details__text">
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Easy Read conversion involves multiple AI services and takes longer than simple translation:
    </p>
    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
      <li>A 2-page document typically takes 2 to 5 minutes</li>
      <li>Image generation is the longest step -- each image takes 10 to 30 seconds</li>
      <li>If the job has been processing for more than 10 minutes, check the Step Functions console for errors</li>
      <li>Try with a shorter document if a long one is timing out</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</details>

<details class="govuk-details">
  <summary class="govuk-details__summary">
    <span class="govuk-details__summary-text">
      Troubleshooting: No images generated
    </span>
  </summary>
  <div class="govuk-details__text">
    <p class="govuk-body">
      If the Easy Read output has simplified text but no images:
    </p>
    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
      <li>The Bedrock model agreement for Nova Canvas may not have been activated -- check the Bedrock console</li>
      <li>Image generation may have failed silently -- the text simplification still works without images</li>
      <li>Check the Step Functions execution for any error steps</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</details>

